  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, wait, wait, wait.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Still I remember I have a group.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I see to save life only how much from the civil people and I see you have a good friend like [?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Hibenuke. ?] He was shot at Ercsi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It is 36 kilometers south of Budapest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And his stomach was, like, open.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he was alive.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we cannot help him because the fire was so hot, so thick, we cannot come.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in the night, I know where he fell.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I come with, with Liashchenko, my friend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I put his coat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We closed his coat to keep it inside him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we put here a fire and schlepped him out from danger till it comes the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where are the Liashchenkos, the Grebeniuks, and the others?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Liashchenko survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the other nice people was falling.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then we have people fall.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We have new people in that time to teach them how to go on with the dynamite.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the one man I see, he couldn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I tell them, take him away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because he would kill himself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the other people were taking out the mines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Then I tell my people listen, stay away from him 25 yards.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And once, I didn't know his name, I give a look.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was flying in the air.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He blew up for carelessness.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And then we come close to the end of the war-- the 8th of May-- yes, like I take-- I told you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I go to this [NON-ENGLISH  SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I saw that there was Jewish homes-- Jewish population in the city.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was a Jewish settlement-- Jewish city.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then comes to the 8th of May.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
